00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:06.810
How to Keep Body Systems in Optimal Shape.

00:00:06.810 --> 00:00:11.019
Keep your body systems in optimal shape so
you can live a long and healthy life.

00:00:11.019 --> 00:00:19.580
You will need Exercise Healthy diet Healthy
weight Stimulation Sunglasses Hormone therapy

00:00:19.580 --> 00:00:29.680
Vitamin D Exfoliating peel Soothing gel Vitamin
C serum Moisturizer with sunscreen Rest and

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:30.680
doctor (optional).

00:00:30.680 --> 00:00:34.160
Don't change your diet without first consulting
your physician.

00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:35.160
Step 1.

00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:40.269
Do all you can to prevent cancer by living
a healthy lifestyle that includes regular

00:00:40.269 --> 00:00:43.269
exercise, a healthy diet, and by maintaining
a healthy weight.

00:00:43.269 --> 00:00:48.850
Aim for 30 to 60 minutes of exercise per day,
and maintain a diet filled with fruits, vegetables,

00:00:48.850 --> 00:00:50.530
and whole grains.

00:00:50.530 --> 00:00:51.769
Step 2.

00:00:51.769 --> 00:00:56.420
Stimulate your mind by learning a new language,
reading a book, taking a class, or starting

00:00:56.420 --> 00:00:58.519
a new hobby that you enjoy.

00:00:58.519 --> 00:00:59.719
Step 3.

00:00:59.719 --> 00:01:05.269
Protect your eyes with sunglasses that have
100 percent UVA or UVB protection.

00:01:05.269 --> 00:01:10.539
Sunglasses can protect you from macular degeneration,
cataracts, and wrinkles around your eyes.

00:01:10.539 --> 00:01:11.549
Step 4.

00:01:11.549 --> 00:01:15.750
Avoid getting sick and prevent the spread
of germs by washing your hands after you use

00:01:15.750 --> 00:01:20.939
a restroom, handle garbage, blow your nose,
and before and after you prepare food.

00:01:20.939 --> 00:01:22.530
Step 5.

00:01:22.530 --> 00:01:26.409
Consider hormone therapy if you are going
through menopause to reduce symptoms such

00:01:26.409 --> 00:01:28.490
as mood swings and night sweats.

00:01:28.490 --> 00:01:32.649
Remain sexually active with your partner to
keep yourself emotionally connected and to

00:01:32.649 --> 00:01:34.490
boost your immune system.

00:01:34.490 --> 00:01:35.600
Step 6.

00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:39.130
Get plenty of vitamin D through sun exposure
or supplements.

00:01:39.130 --> 00:01:44.030
Studies show that prostate cancer, colon cancer,
and breast cancer may be linked to vitamin

00:01:44.030 --> 00:01:45.030
D deficiencies.

00:01:45.030 --> 00:01:48.280
Ask your doctor if you need a supplement.

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:49.450
Step 7.

00:01:49.450 --> 00:01:53.929
Keep your skin looking young and healthy by
using an exfoliating peel followed by a soothing

00:01:53.929 --> 00:01:54.929
gel.

00:01:54.929 --> 00:01:58.760
Use a vitamin C serum and a moisturizer with
sunscreen to protect your skin.

00:01:58.760 --> 00:02:04.100
Stay healthy by keeping your body rested by
getting 7 to 8 hours of sleep every night.

00:02:04.100 --> 00:02:09.159
Did you know The average age an American women
goes through menopause is 51.

